{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"34929-nin-hian-nungkheuong","title":"ນິນຮຽນນຸ່ງເຄື່ອງ","description":"ເຊົ້າມື້ໜຶ່ງນິນຢາກນຸ່ງຊຸດນັກຮຽນ ແຕ່ວ່າໃຜໆກໍຄາວຽກບໍ່ສາມາດ ຊ່ວຍລາວໄດ້! ແມ່ຂອງລາວຄາແຕ່ງກິນ, ພໍ່ຂອງລາວຄາເກືອໄກ່, ແມ່ຕູ້ຄາກວາດເດີ່ນບ້ານ. ນິນຈະນຸ່ງເຄື່ອງໄດ້ບໍ?","language":"Lao","langCode":"lo","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Bounhome  Khensonema"],"illustrators":["Aphisith Souphavongtay"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/34929-nin-hian-nungkheuong"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93891/size3/827ac2f61721dcdd027c7bfade890546.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93891/size6/827ac2f61721dcdd027c7bfade890546.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69183/size6/55a276deeae8b36c14a1b4d24b4cacdd.jpg","text":"ມື້ນີ້ເປີດສົກຮຽນໃໝ່.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69184/size6/8fbbc845b1e1a2b0675ba4b25234e354.jpg","text":"ນິນນຸ່ງເຄື່ອງເອງບໍ່ເປັນ \nລາວແລ່ນໄປຫາແມ່.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69185/size6/c1a92e6b7a2654298a8b1c3379654ec5.jpg","text":"“ແມ່! ຊ່ວຍນຸ່ງເຄື່ອງ ໃຫ້ລູກແດ່!”\n“ແມ່ແຕ່ງກິນແລ້ວ ແມ່ຈະນຸ່ງໃຫ້”","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69186/size6/7240b5230afb286fad186172b69db118.jpg","text":"ນິນເລີຍແລ່ນອອກນອກເຮືອນ ເພື່ອໄປຫາຄົນອື່ນນຸ່ງເຄື່ອງໃຫ້.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69187/size6/1464a27057fa5774ddbbd8a8a6b96135.jpg","text":"“ພໍ່! ຊ່ວຍນຸ່ງເຄື່ອງໃຫ້ລູກແດ່!”\n“ພໍ່ຍັງຄາເກືອໄກ່ຢູ່, ເກືອໄກ່ແລ້ວພໍ່ຈະນຸ່ງໃຫ້”.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69188/size6/423b1b52495e0ae63c339a34858b2e5b.jpg","text":"“ພໍ່ຕູ້! ນຸ່ງເຄື່ອງໃຫ້ຫຼານແດ່”\n“ພ່ໍຕູ້ເອົາຄວາຍໄປລ່າມກ່ອນ, ພ່ໍຕູ້ກັບມາ ແລ້ວຈະນຸ່ງໃຫ້”.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69190/size6/b92bedaed8df6d0f6a3369fe89fd7b19.jpg","text":"“ແມ່ຕູ້! ນຸ່ງເຄື່ອງໃຫ້ຫຼານແດ່”\n“ແມ່ຕູ້ຄາກວາດໃບໄມ້ຢູ່, ຈັກໜ້ອຍແມ່ຕູ້ຈະນຸ່ງໃຫ້”.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69191/size6/9c7cda73969abda9665ca3a1bb2a34a4.jpg","text":"“ອ້າຍຫຼ້າ! ນຸ່ງເຄື່ອງໃຫ້ນ້ອງແດ່”\n“ອ້າຍຈະໄປຕັກນໍ້າແລ້ວກ່ອນ ແລ້ວຈະໄປນຸ່ງໃຫ້”.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69192/size6/f2368fb4d91776359934aab11e5ffd04.jpg","text":"“ບໍ່ມີໃຜວ່າງນຸ່ງເຄື່ອງໃຫ້ນິນ”.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69193/size6/a7d90871da625159a8ddd74e5bdc5164.jpg","text":"ທຸກຄົນຕ່າງກໍຄາວຽກ ນິນຄິດຫຍັງບໍ່ອອກ.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69194/size6/a9ba209fb517d9c7d565971de1d22b05.jpg","text":"ນິນນຸ່ງເຄື່ອງເອງ! \nນິນນຸ່ງເຄື່ອງ ມະຍຸມະຍະ\nນິນນຸ່ງຜິດດ້ານ.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69195/size6/845225f312010fa3fc7b1e720f450618.jpg","text":"ໃສ່ເກີບບໍ່ຖືກເບຶ້ື້ອງ.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69196/size6/ebd3a423130bd39a45898bb8ace0f1b3.jpg","text":"ແຍງແວ່ນເບິ່ງ ຜັດນຸ່ງເຄື່ອງຜິດດ້ານ\nພໍ່ແມ່ຂອງນິນທີ່ຈອບເບິ່ງກໍຫົວຂວັນ.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69197/size6/ef645c6085165a3667b0d316557b66e8.jpg","text":"“ແມ່ຈະຊ່ວຍນຸ່ງໃຫ້\nອ້າຍຈະຊ່ວຍ, ພໍ່ກໍຈະຊ່ວຍ”","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69199/size6/11cc6d3d225dc963d85bbdb9324ea600.jpg","text":"ຕອນນີ້ນິນກຽມພ້ອມທີ່ຈະໄປໂຮງຮຽນແລ້ວ.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":15,"words":42}}